				<td colspan="2"><span>I currently 2 box with a 65 shaman and a 54 bard, with the bard tanking the mobs and chanting them down.  I haven't had too much of a problem with the bard tanking, provided that I get the shaman slow to land quickly.  I've boxed a lower level cleric as well and CH is great, but a 75% slow is hard to beat.  Particularly at 65 when the shaman gets Quiesence.
<br />

<br />
I'm sure this strategy will stop working eventually, when it does I'll just group more<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

