				<td colspan="2"><span>I asked around on some Druid and Cleric boards and basically verified things that have been said here.  One interesting note was that several people advised that a Bard should do some light tanking in addition to kiting so that combat skills stay up.  Apparently other classes expect a plate wearing, dual wielding bard to be able to mix it up with the mobs<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> 
